{"tid":559953,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[香港代表出戰喇]17-18 LIHKG環球女神冠軍盃16強首回合投選專區 #姬嘉鐸 #娜璉 #朱千雪 #正美","createTime":"2018-02-13T15:59:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-14T14:02:18.000Z","uid":92376,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f9f8ecb00810d711e49a18a880a65d754da7644e","tid":559953,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T15:59:32.000Z","msg":"以下為即將舉行之賽事<br />\n會員可留意稍後時間發出的比賽專用回覆並以回覆評分功能進行投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(唔識點樣用回覆評分功能黎投票既巴打可以參考下面既教學)<br />\n<br />\n由首場12:00am開始,每兩分鐘開賽一場<br />\n<br />\nGal Gadot v 林娜璉@TWICE<br />\n朱千雪 v 長澤正美<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/hiNda68.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FhiNda68.png&h=d4221617&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/s2sfX8L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fs2sfX8L.png&h=b53ffa65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/fg4vwe7.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Ffg4vwe7.png&d=DyFP53Hn%2F%2F%2BzStwfSKSx2ywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=873e94b6\" target=\"_blank\">http://i.imgur.com/fg4vwe7.png</a><br />\n有關主場指定額外得分情況,請參閱主場額外分數增幅表<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f83ca2eeac5db27454f8bd0a52abb636e38816e","tid":559953,"uid":92376,"like":67,"dislike":48,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T15:59:59.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2017-18 LIHKG環球女神冠軍盃16強首回合</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2018-2-14 12am-10pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/4xA95hR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F4xA95hR.png&h=339493ad&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/BDX7QJw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FBDX7QJw.png&h=baa0a1fc&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/8O41HKp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F8O41HKp.png&h=66d92b33&s={SIZE}\" />Gal Gadot v 林娜璉@TWICE<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/sbXOEPJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FsbXOEPJ.png&h=d2608c71&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">環冠盃淘汰賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以回覆評分功能(前者上箭咀;後者下箭咀)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆評分功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">兩回合賽事設作客十進一優惠，作客女神每得十分可再獲一分。額外分數會獨立計算，如總比分賽和將會按照雙方額外分數多寡以決定勝負。若依然賽和則會每次加時十分鐘，直至分出勝負為止，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"c5a84a5c50f50081ddeb764837e1e2da35c4379a","tid":559953,"uid":92376,"like":87,"dislike":46,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T16:01:59.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2018-2-14 12:02am-10:02pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/2ikrGhT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F2ikrGhT.png&h=917b5654&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ylbvCO9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FylbvCO9.png&h=0b309a32&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/0Q6FBnk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F0Q6FBnk.png&h=ded63cd8&s={SIZE}\" />朱千雪 v 長澤正美<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/fDKJUOh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FfDKJUOh.png&h=c6bfb075&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">環冠盃淘汰賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以回覆評分功能(前者上箭咀;後者下箭咀)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆評分功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">兩回合賽事設作客十進一優惠，作客女神每得十分可再獲一分。額外分數會獨立計算，如總比分賽和將會按照雙方額外分數多寡以決定勝負。若依然賽和則會每次加時十分鐘，直至分出勝負為止，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"e99a820da4e25f4b1d5e9d770d3fb330c2e99489","tid":559953,"uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T16:03:52.000Z","msg":"唐嫣 v 新垣結衣<br />\n首回合: 2月21日 <br />\n<br />\nEmma Watson v 林宣妤<br />\n首回合: 2月21日<br />\n<br />\n謝安琪 v 名井南@TWICE<br />\n首回合: 2月20日<br />\n<br />\n平井桃@TWICE v 林明禎<br />\n首回合: 2月20日 <br />\n<br />\n下星期一二繼續有另外四場環冠盃16強首回合,實力十分強橫既新垣結衣都會出場,記得留意啦"},{"pid":"b990402520340e079d62e9eb818ea75e433b7454","tid":559953,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T16:05:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a14bad4c140f9154fca6c194e4b8dfe0a0188a4","tid":559953,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T16:06:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28118df6d81841d57189dcbd4fffcdfdcccf0daf","tid":559953,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T16:08:28.000Z","msg":"今晚好似好睇過尋日咁"},{"pid":"5ef5568fc0a1ddadef8cc84fcb3423a74bf7b883","tid":559953,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T16:09:16.000Z","msg":"來自中東或者遠歐既Gal Gadot竟然領先緊韓國女團大將<br />\n有趣呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f597456adf688d28fea57bb20e19c33e50dd1813","tid":559953,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T16:10:13.000Z","msg":"朱千雪對住日本十分知名既選手長澤正美暫時仲處上風,唔知應